      "item": "ItemSpec",
      "reviewed": false,
      "intent": "Model a code-item spec entry with item name, intent string, source_span, and optional fields (reviewed, tree_path, source_hash, source_anchor, confidence, related, _hints). Enforce deny_unknown_fields and skip serializing None optionals. _hints holds transient inference aids from liyi init, stripped by check --fix.",
